                summary: 'Distress flare sighted approx 10nm off the coast of Chennai.',
                location: '13.08° N, 80.27° E',
                time: '1 hr ago',
                description: 'A single red distress flare was reported by a commercial vessel. No corresponding distress call has been received. Coast guard has been notified to investigate.',
